snippet.description:
🎯 LIVE IND vs PAK | Asia Cup 2025 Match 6 | Live Score & Hindi Commentary
🏆India vs Pakistan | Asia Cup 2025 Match 6 | Live Score & Hindi Commentary
🔥 Streamed exclusively on 1iQ Gaming — your destination for Asia Cup 2025 showdown, real-time scores & explosive Hindi commentary with Cricket 24 visuals!

📌 Match Details:
🏟️ Venue: Dubai International Cricket Stadium, UAE
📅 Date: September 14, 2025 – Match 6, Group A
🏏 Format: T20 International – Asia Cup 2025
🎯 One of cricket’s fiercest rivalries returns: India vs Pakistan – expectations, tension & massive crowd attention.

👥 Probable Playing XIs:

🇮🇳 India XI: Abhishek Sharma, Shubman Gill, Suryakumar Yadav (C), Tilak Varma, Sanju Samson (wk), Shivam Dube, Hardik Pandya, Axar Patel, Kuldeep Yadav, Jasprit Bumrah, Varun Chakravarthy 

🇵🇰 Pakistan XI: Sahibzada Farhan, Saim Ayub, Fakhar Zaman, Salmaan Ali Agha (C), Hasan Nawaz, Mohammad Haris (wk), Mohammad Nawaz, Faheem Ashraf, Shaheen Shah Afridi, Sufiyan Muqeem, Abrar Ahmed 


🌤️ Pitch & Weather Report:

Pitch: Balanced wicket at Dubai, helpers for spin in middle overs; pacers get early rewards. 

average first-innings score here ~ 149. 

Weather: Clear skies expected, temperature high (~39.1°C IST), dry conditions. 


📝 Match Context / What to Watch:

India enters on strong form after a dominant win over UAE. Pakistan beat Oman convincingly. Both want vital Group A points. 

With Virat Kohli absent, India depend on Suryakumar Yadav, Shubman Gill, and the spin trio (Kuldeep, Varun Chakaravarthy, Axar) to control the middle overs. 

Pak’s batting threats: Mohammad Haris, Fakhar Zaman; their bowling led by Shaheen Afridi needs to strike early. 

Toss could be important — team batting first might get edge due to dew later in the innings.

हो कैसे आऊ मिलवे बजेंगे कंगना 
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

हा आवे तो आजा झूठी बात क्यों बनावे,,
दो महीना से रानी येठ क्यों दिखावे 

हा बात बनावे बैठी बैठी अंगना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जावे संजना,,

हा करले सवर बाबू मिलने भी आऊंगी,,
प्यार की है प्यास पानी हाथ से पिलाऊंगी,,

प्यार से बडो कोई रोग हतना,,
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

न चहिए प्यार मोकू बारिश की बूंद को,,
छाती से लगाके देजा मौकु सकून सो,,

हा खून सो जलावे गोरी तेरा हंसना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जाएंगे सजना,,

Ho kese aau milve bajenge kangna,,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna 

Aave to aaja jhuti baat Kyo banave,,
Do mahina se rani yeth kyo dikhave,,
Ha baat banave bethi bethi angana,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna

Ha karle savar babu milne bhi aaungi ,,
Pyar ki hai pyas pani hath se pilaungi,,,
Pyar se bdo koi rog hath na,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna,,

N chahiye pyar moku barish ki bund ko,,
Chhati se lagake deja moku sakun so,,

khoon  so jalave gori tera hasna,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna,,,

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films’ Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story…and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question…do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

The end is near. Crunchyroll is excited to bring Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle to theaters as an epic trilogy event! Get tickets now! https://got.cr/cc-dsknym

It is the Taisho Period in Japan. Tanjiro, a kindhearted boy who sells charcoal for a living, finds his family slaughtered by a demon. To make matters worse, his younger sister Nezuko, the sole survivor, has been transformed into a demon herself.

Though devastated by this grim reality, Tanjiro resolves to become a “demon slayer” so that he can turn his sister back into a human, and kill the demon that massacred his family.

snippet.title: #Video | जितिया गीत 2025 | Jitiya Parab | JITIYA SONG 2025 | Anjali Bharti | Bhojpuri #Jitiya Geet
snippet.description:
#jitya_vrat_katha #anudubey #jitiya_geet
jitiya vrat katha,jitiya ke geet,jitiya song,jitiya ka gana,jitiya katha,jitiya geet,jitiya ke katha,jitiya status,जितिया व्रत कथा,जितिया - चील सियारिन की कहानी,jitiya story in hindi,jitiya story,jitiya video song,jitiya ka video,anu dubey,anu dubey bhakti song,jitiya bhojpuri song,जिउतिया व्रत,jiutiya geet,जिउतिया व्रत स्पेशल गीत,जितिया गीत,jitiya song 2021,jitiya ke gana bhojpuri mein,jitiya geet video,jitiya geet maithili,jitiya kab hai

_____________________________________________________________________

क्या है पौराणिक कथा: धार्मिक कथाओं के मुताबिक बताया जाता है कि एक विशाल
पाकड़ के पेड़ पर एक चील रहती थी। उसे पेड़ के नीचे एक सियारिन भी रहती थी। दोनों पक्की सहेलियां थीं, दोनों ने कुछ महिलाओं को देखकर जितिया व्रत करने का संकल्प लिया और भगवान श्री जीऊतवाहन की पूजा और व्रत करने का प्रण ले लिया।

लेकिन जिस दिन दोनों को व्रत रखना था, उसी दिन शहर के एक बड़े व्यापारी की मृत्यु हो गई और उसके दाह संस्कार में सियारिन को भूख लगने लगी थी। मुर्दा देखकर वह खुद को रोक न सकी और उसका व्रत टूट गया। पर चील ने संयम रखा और नियम व श्रद्धा से अगले दिन व्रत का पारण किया।

अगले जन्म में दोनों सहेलियों ने ब्राह्मण परिवार में पुत्री के रूप में जन्म लिया। उनके पिता का नाम भास्कर था। चील, बड़ी बहन बनी और सिया‍रन, छोटी बहन के रूप में जन्‍मीं। चील का नाम शीलवती रखा गया, शीलवती की शादी बुद्धिसेन के साथ हुई। जबकि सियारिन का नाम कपुरावती रखा गया और उसकी शादी उस नगर के राजा मलायकेतु से हुई।

भगवान जीऊतवाहन के आशीर्वाद से शीलवती के सात बेटे हुए। पर कपुरावती के सभी बच्चे जन्म लेते ही मर जाते थे। कुछ समय बाद शीलवती के सातों पुत्र बड़े हो गए और वे सभी राजा के दरबार में काम करने लगे। कपुरावती के मन में उन्‍हें देख इर्ष्या की भावना आ गयी, उसने राजा से कहकर सभी बेटों के सर काट दिए।

उन्‍हें सात नए बर्तन मंगवाकर उसमें रख दिया और लाल कपड़े से ढककर शीलवती के पास भिजवा दिया। यह देख भगवान जीऊतवाहन ने मिट्टी से सातों भाइयों के सिर बनाए और सभी के सिरों को उसके धड़ से जोड़कर उन पर अमृत छिड़क दिया। इससे उनमें जान आ गई।

सातों युवक जिंदा हो गए और घर लौट आए, जो कटे सिर रानी ने भेजे थे वे फल बन गए। दूसरी ओर रानी कपुरावती, बुद्धिसेन के घर से सूचना पाने को व्याकुल थी। जब काफी देर सूचना नहीं आई तो कपुरावती स्वयं बड़ी बहन के घर गयी। वहां सबको जिंदा देखकर वह सन्न रह गयी, जब उसे होश आया तो बहन को उसने सारी बात बताई। अब उसे अपनी गलती पर पछतावा हो रहा था, भगवान जीऊतवाहन की कृपा से शीलवती को पूर्व जन्म की बातें याद आ गईं। वह कपुरावती को लेकर उसी पाकड़ के पेड़ के पास गयी और उसे सारी बातें बताईं। कपुरावती बेहोश हो गई और मर गई, जब राजा को इसकी खबर मिली तो उन्‍होंने उसी जगह पर जाकर पाकड़ के पेड़ के नीचे कपुरावती का दाह-संस्कार कर दिया।

सातों युवक जिंदा हो गए और घर लौट आए, जो कटे सिर रानी ने भेजे थे वे फल बन गए। दूसरी ओर रानी कपुरावती, बुद्धिसेन के घर से सूचना पाने को व्याकुल थी। जब काफी देर सूचना नहीं आई तो कपुरावती स्वयं बड़ी बहन के घर गयी। वहां सबको जिंदा देखकर वह सन्न रह गयी, जब उसे होश आया तो बहन को उसने सारी बात बताई। अब उसे अपनी गलती पर पछतावा हो रहा था, भगवान जीऊतवाहन की कृपा से शीलवती को पूर्व जन्म की बातें याद आ गईं। वह कपुरावती को लेकर उसी पाकड़ के पेड़ के पास गयी और उसे सारी बातें बताईं। कपुरावती बेहोश हो गई और मर गई, जब राजा को इसकी खबर मिली तो उन्‍होंने उसी जगह पर जाकर पाकड़ के पेड़ के नीचे कपुरावती का दाह-संस्कार कर दिया।

ಹಾಡು : ಗಂಗಿ ಗಂಗಿ ಗಂಗಿ 
ಪಲ್ಲವಿ: 
ಗಂಡು: 
ಉಟ್ಟದಿ ನೀನು ತೆಳ್ಳನೆ ಲಂಗ ನೋಡಿರೆ ಸಾಕು ಬೆನ್ಹತ್ತಂಗ ಗಂಗಿ.. 
ಅದಿಯ ನೀನು ಪೂರಾ ಯಂಗ, 
ಯದಿಯ ಒಳಗ ಜುಮ್ಮ ಅನ್ನುವಂಗ 
ಗಂಗಿ ಯೆ ಗಂಗಿ 
ಹೆಣ್ಣು: 
ನನ್ನ ನೋಡಿ ನೋಡಿ ನೀನು.. ಮೈಯಾಕ ಮುರೀತಿ.. 
ಮುಚ್ಚಿಇಟ್ಟ ಆಸೇಎಲ್ಲಾಕಣ್ಣಾಗ ಸುರೀತಿ.. 
ಗಂಡಾ ಗುಂಡಿ ಅಗುನು ಬಾರೋಮಾವ ಒಂದು ಸರತಿ.. 
ಗಂಡು: 
ಗಂಗಿ ಗಂಗಿ ಗಂಗಿ 
ನೀಜಗ್ಗಬ್ಯಾಡ ಲುಂಗಿ.. 
ಚರಣ: 1 
ಹೆಣ್ಣು: 
ಗುಂಪಿನ್ಯಾಗ ಬಂದ ನನ್ನ ಸೊಂಟಾ ಯಾಕ್ ಹಿಂಡತಿ 
ಮೀಸಿ ತೀರವಕೊಂತ ಬಂದ ಯದಿ ಯದರ ನಿಲ್ಲತಿ 
ಗಂಡು: 
ಯಸ್ಟ ಬೆಳ್ಳಗ ಅದಾವ ಹುಡಗಿ ನಿನ್ನ ಕೈಯ ಕಾಲ 
ಒನ್ದ ಒಂದ ಕಪ್ಪ ಚುಕ್ಕಿಐತಿ ಸೊಂಟದ ಮ್ಯಾಲ.. 
ಹೆಣ್ಣು; 
ನೀಕಚ್ಚುಬಾರೋಗಲ್ಲಾ
ನಾ ವಲ್ಯಾಅನ್ನೂದಿಲ್ಲಾ.. 
ಗಂಡು: 
ಈ ಗುಂಡ ಗುಂಡನ ಗಲ್ಲಾ
ನಮ್ ಜಿಲ್ಲಾದಾಗ ಇಲ್ಲ 
ಹೆಣ್ಣು: 
ಮತ್ತ ತಡಾ ಯಾಕ ಮಾವ ಕೊಡಬಾರೋಬೆಲ್ಲಾ
ಗಂಡು: 

ಏ.. ಗಂಗಿ ಗಂಗಿ.. 
ಚರಣ: 2 
ಹೆಣ್ಣು: 
ನೀ ಉಡಾಳ ಇದ್ರೂಊರ ತುಂಬಾ ಹವಾ ಭಾಳ ಇಟ್ಟದಿ.. 
ಮಂದಿ ಇದ್ರೂಮೀಸಿ ಚುಚ್ಚುವಂಗ ಮುತ್ತ ಕೊಟ್ಟದಿ 
ಗಂಡು : 
ಊರಿಗ ಊರ ಐತಿ ಹುಡಗಿ ನನ್ನ ಮ್ಯಾನೇಜದಾಗ 
ನಿನಗ ಯಾರರ ಏನಾರ ಅಂದರ ಹೇಳ ಕಳಸತನ ಮ್ಯಾಗ 
ಹೆಣ್ಣು: 
ನೀಅದಿ ಬಲು ಘಾಟಿ.. 
ನಿನಗ ಯಾರು ಇಲ್ಲ ಸಾಟಿ 
ಗಂಡು : 
ನಾ ತಿಂದ ಬೆಳದನ ರೊಟ್ಟಿ
ನೀನೋಡ ಒಮ್ಮಿಮುಟ್ಟಿ
ಹೆಣ್ಣು: 
ಅಂದ ಚಂದ ಯಲ್ಲ ನಿಂದ ಮಾಡಿಕೊರೊಲೂಟಿ 
ಗಂಡು: 
ಏ.. ಗಂಗಿ ಗಂಗಿ.. 
…………………………………..

snippet.title: WEDNESDAY SEASON 3 – First Trailer | Jenna Ortega, Lady Gaga | Netflix
snippet.description:
— Attention Viewers ⚠️
— This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
— WEDNESDAY SEASON 3

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

— In this concept trailer for Wednesday Season 3, the story continues in the aftermath of Season 2 as Wednesday finds herself entangled in an even darker web of family curses and rising threats. Hidden beneath Grandmama Hester’s watch, Aunt Ophelia resurfaces with a chilling prophecy that Wednesday must die, while Professor Capri and Tyler rally a growing army of Hydes to wage war against Nevermore. At the same time, Enid has vanished into the wilderness, lost to her werewolf form, forcing Wednesday on a relentless search that blurs the line between friend and foe. As ancestral secrets unravel and enemies close in, Wednesday must confront not only the cult determined to claim her bloodline but also the possibility that destiny itself has marked her for destruction. With higher stakes, fractured alliances, and a promise of unrelenting darkness, this new chapter teases a battle where survival may demand the ultimate sacrifice.

snippet.description:

asia cup 2025 india vs pakistan

India vs Pakistan Asia Cup 2025
Live Cricket Match Today 
Cricket Live 
Live
Asia Cup Live 
Asia Cup 2025 Live

When: Sunday, September 14, 2025 at 6:30 PM local time / 8:00 PM IST

Where: Dubai International Stadium

What to expect: One of the center pitches on the square is being readied for this match. The pitch, as Shivam Dube reckoned after the UAE match, could again be on the slower side, with spinners expected to have more say as the tournament wears on. It's supposed to be a kinder day heat wise, with high temperatures of 39 degrees expected. Dew could still be a factor later in the night, so expect the captain winning the toss to chase.

Team news

India: Ryan ten Doeschate reckoned that India didn't gain "too much information" from their first Asia Cup outing but seemed to suggest that the combinations are likely to stick. That could mean Sanju Samson and Shivam Dube in the middle-order once nire, no Arshdeep Singh, and more game time together for Kuldeep Yadav and Varun Chakaravarthy.

Injuries/unavailability: Shubman Gill was hit in the nets during the optional session on match eve but the Indian vice-captain resumed his batting after a brief timeout and looked alright.

Tactics & matchups: Sanju Samson in the middle order hasn't quite worked before. In T20Is since 2021, Samson has averaged 24 and struck at 139 when batting No.4 or below. His corresponding numbers while batting in the top-three are roughly 37 and 148 respectively. asia cup 2025 live

Pakistan: Salman Agha's side is also likely to go in unchanged after their convincing victory in the opening match.

Injuries/unavailability: The entire squad is available to pick from.

Tactics & matchups: Mohammad Nawaz, who was the Player of the Series in each of Pakistan's last two T20I series wins, will be key with the ball. He has averaged under 15 and conceded at under seven an over in each of the four series he's featured in, in 2025.

Probable XI: Saim Ayub, Sahibzada Farhan, Mohammad Haris(w), Fakhar Zaman, Salman Agha(c), Hasan Nawaz, Mohammad Nawaz, Faheem Ashraf, Shaheen Afridi, Sufiyan Muqeem, Abrar Ahmed

🔴Live: India vs Pakistan, T20 Asia Cup 2025 | Live Cricket Match Today | IND vs PAK Live Scores

India vs Pakistan Asia Cup 2025
Live Cricket Match Today 
Cricket Live 
Live
Asia Cup Live 
Asia Cup 2025 Live

When: Sunday, September 14, 2025 at 6:30 PM local time / 8:00 PM IST

Where: Dubai International Stadium

What to expect: One of the center pitches on the square is being readied for this match. The pitch, as Shivam Dube reckoned after the UAE match, could again be on the slower side, with spinners expected to have more say as the tournament wears on. It's supposed to be a kinder day heat wise, with high temperatures of 39 degrees expected. Dew could still be a factor later in the night, so expect the captain winning the toss to chase.

Team news

India: Ryan ten Doeschate reckoned that India didn't gain "too much information" from their first Asia Cup outing but seemed to suggest that the combinations are likely to stick. That could mean Sanju Samson and Shivam Dube in the middle-order once nire, no Arshdeep Singh, and more game time together for Kuldeep Yadav and Varun Chakaravarthy.

Injuries/unavailability: Shubman Gill was hit in the nets during the optional session on match eve but the Indian vice-captain resumed his batting after a brief timeout and looked alright.

Tactics & matchups: Sanju Samson in the middle order hasn't quite worked before. In T20Is since 2021, Samson has averaged 24 and struck at 139 when batting No.4 or below. His corresponding numbers while batting in the top-three are roughly 37 and 148 respectively. asia cup 2025 live

Probable XI: Abhishek Sharma, Shubman Gill, Suryakumar Yadav(c), Tilak Varma, Sanju Samson(w), Shivam Dube, Hardik Pandya, Axar Patel, Kuldeep Yadav, Jasprit Bumrah, Varun Chakaravarthy

Pakistan: Salman Agha's side is also likely to go in unchanged after their convincing victory in the opening match.

Injuries/unavailability: The entire squad is available to pick from.

Tactics & matchups: Mohammad Nawaz, who was the Player of the Series in each of Pakistan's last two T20I series wins, will be key with the ball. He has averaged under 15 and conceded at under seven an over in each of the four series he's featured in, in 2025.

Probable XI: Saim Ayub, Sahibzada Farhan, Mohammad Haris(w), Fakhar Zaman, Salman Agha(c), Hasan Nawaz, Mohammad Nawaz, Faheem Ashraf, Shaheen Afridi, Sufiyan Muqeem, Abrar Ahmed


India vs Pakistan, 6th T20I Match of the Asia Cup 2025 is going to be played at Abu Dhabi International Cricket Stadium UAE.

snippet.title: LIGHT CAMERA ACTION I Official trailer I Bodo film 2025 I Sangeena Brahma,Anjali Daimari,Jayanta Nzy
snippet.description:
ZaiZoog CineVerse Pvt Ltd. alongwith Sunswarang Khakhlary Films are thrilled to announce the release of our upcoming Bodo movie 'LiCA' this Puja season! Get ready to dive into the zeal of filmmaking to celebrate friendship, love, honor and family amidst betrayal & revenge lurking in the shadows. Grab your tickets to witness the chaos around the battling opponents. 

Starring Sangeena Brahma, Anjali Daimary, Jayanta Narzary and Golerius Murmu this is the ultimate BTS drama, a refreshing take, packed with unfiltered humor, unexpected twists, and a whole new level of storytelling.

snippet.title: जितिया व्रत आरती - Jivitputrika Vrat Aarti - Jitiya Vrat 2025 - Jitiya Vrat Ki Aarti
snippet.description:
🌸 जितिया व्रत आरती (Jivitputrika Vrat Aarti) का विशेष महत्व है। माताएं अपने पुत्र की दीर्घायु, स्वास्थ्य और सुख-समृद्धि के लिए यह व्रत करती हैं। 2025 के जितिया व्रत अवसर पर प्रस्तुत यह आरती श्रद्धालुओं को भक्ति और आस्था से जोड़ती है। इस आरती का पाठ करने से घर में शांति, सौभाग्य और परिवार में सुख-समृद्धि आती है। 🙏
✨ सुनें और भक्तिभाव से आरती का आनंद लें।

Subscribe us :- @spirtualactivity 

Make Reels on Instagram :-
https://www.instagram.com/reels/audio/790084683415602/

जय श्रीजीमूत वाहन प्रभु जय श्री जीमूत वाहन
रक्षक बन सन्तान के 2  करे सबका  पालन,जय श्रीजीमूत... 
आश्विन कृष्ण की अष्टमी व्रत तेरा जो करे 
प्रभु व्रत तेरा जो करे 
सुख समृद्धि धन धान्य से घर भंडार भरे ,जय श्री जीमूत ...
जो व्रत निर्जला रखते, दुःख संकट कटते  
प्रभु दुःख संकट कटते 
चिंता मिटे उसी की जो जो तेरा नाम जपते ,जय श्री ...
माता बहने सहोदर ध्यान तेरा जो धरे 
प्रभु ध्यान तेरा जो धरे 
तेरी कृपा से बाबा भवसागर वो तरे ,जय श्री जीमूत ...
धुप दीप नैवेद्य से जो करते पूजन 
स्वामी जो करते पूजन 
जनम जन्म के उनके कट जाते बंधन,जय ....
कुश दुर्वा और अक्षत, पान सुपारी चढ़े 
प्रभु पान सुपारी चढ़े 
विधि विधान से पूजे, चन्द्र सा भाग्य बढ़े ,जय श्री  ...
जो श्री जीमूत वाहनजी की, आरती हैं करते
तेरी आरती जो करते  
काल भी उस द्वारे पर  2 आने से डरते 

Jai Shree Jeemoot Vahan Prabhu Jai Shree Jeemoot Vahan
Rakshak ban santaan ke, kare sabka paalan, Jai Shree Jeemoot...

Ashwin Krishna ki Ashtami vrat tera jo kare,
Prabhu vrat tera jo kare,
Sukh samriddhi dhan dhaanya se ghar bhandaar bhare, Jai Shree Jeemoot...

Jo vrat nirjala rakhte, dukh sankat katte,
Prabhu dukh sankat katte,
Chinta mite usi ki jo jo tera naam japte, Jai Shree...

Mata bahane sahodar dhyaan tera jo dhare,
Prabhu dhyaan tera jo dhare,
Teri kripa se Baba bhavsagar vo tare, Jai Shree Jeemoot...

Dhoop deep naivedya se jo karte poojan,
Swami jo karte poojan,
Janam janm ke unke kat jaate bandhan, Jai...

Kush durva aur akshat, paan supari chadhe,
Prabhu paan supari chadhe,
Vidhi vidhaan se pooje, Chandra sa bhaagya badhe, Jai Shree...

Jo Shree Jeemoot Vahan ji ki aarti hai karte,
Teri aarti jo karte,
Kaal bhi us dvaare par aane se darte.

👉 Subscribe Now: https://www.youtube.com/@spirtualactivity/featured
👉 Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Spiritualactivity/

सुख समृद्धि धन धान्य से घर भंडार भरे ,जय श्री जीमूत ...
जो व्रत निर्जला रखते, दुःख संकट कटते  
प्रभु दुःख संकट कटते 
चिंता मिटे उसी की जो जो तेरा नाम जपते ,जय श्री ...
माता बहने सहोदर ध्यान तेरा जो धरे 
प्रभु ध्यान तेरा जो धरे 
तेरी कृपा से बाबा भवसागर वो तरे ,जय श्री जीमूत ...
धुप दीप नैवेद्य से जो करते पूजन 
स्वामी जो करते पूजन 
जनम जन्म के उनके कट जाते बंधन,जय ....
कुश दुर्वा और अक्षत, पान सुपारी चढ़े 
प्रभु पान सुपारी चढ़े 
विधि विधान से पूजे, चन्द्र सा भाग्य बढ़े ,जय श्री  ...
जो श्री जीमूत वाहनजी की, आरती हैं करते
तेरी आरती जो करते  
काल भी उस द्वारे पर  2 आने से डरते 

Jai Shree Jeemoot Vahan Prabhu Jai Shree Jeemoot Vahan
Rakshak ban santaan ke, kare sabka paalan, Jai Shree Jeemoot...

Ashwin Krishna ki Ashtami vrat tera jo kare,
Prabhu vrat tera jo kare,
Sukh samriddhi dhan dhaanya se ghar bhandaar bhare, Jai Shree Jeemoot...

Jo vrat nirjala rakhte, dukh sankat katte,
Prabhu dukh sankat katte,
Chinta mite usi ki jo jo tera naam japte, Jai Shree...

Mata bahane sahodar dhyaan tera jo dhare,
Prabhu dhyaan tera jo dhare,
Teri kripa se Baba bhavsagar vo tare, Jai Shree Jeemoot...

Dhoop deep naivedya se jo karte poojan,
Swami jo karte poojan,
Janam janm ke unke kat jaate bandhan, Jai...

Kush durva aur akshat, paan supari chadhe,
Prabhu paan supari chadhe,
Vidhi vidhaan se pooje, Chandra sa bhaagya badhe, Jai Shree...

Jo Shree Jeemoot Vahan ji ki aarti hai karte,
Teri aarti jo karte,
Kaal bhi us dvaare par aane se darte.

snippet.title: TOCHAN KING Kave Tere Yaar Ne | CK NARA | NISHU DESHWAL | ROHIT DESHWAL
snippet.description:
Song - Tochan King Kave Tere Yaar Ne
Singer/Lyrics/Composer - CK NARA
Artist - Nishu Deshwal,Rohit Deshwal
Music - Mintu Bhardwaj 
Label - CK NARA
                                   TEAM NISHU DESHWAL
Lyrics:-

Chaude Chaude Tyre Lera Kaali Thar Ke
Chhora John Deere Gail Yo Drift Maar De
Khali Hojya Se Maidaan Fer Aajya Se Tufaan Jit Hoke Khada Pat Pe Re Thaapi Maar De
Koi Karjya Na Chook Re Bana Rya Se Mashook Chhora Hathyar Ne

Tochan King Kave Tere Yaar Ne Re Gori Tere Yaar Ne
Tochan King Kave Tere Yaar Ne Re Gori Tere Yaar Ne

Haryana Ke Me Aake Zila Panipat Dhora Mera Gaam Puch Le
Tochan King Chhora Nishu Deshwal Kite Naam Puch Le
Milna Se Bhai Rohit Deshwal Te Ra Bheed Laagi Baarne 

Tochan King Kave Tere Yaar Ne Re Gori Tere Yaar Ne
Tochan King Kave Tere Yaar Ne Re Gori Tere Yaar Ne

Sadka Pe Dole Raani Dhool Thaandi Baan Me Jyu Saanp Bhaaje Re
Fortuner Me Chaale Jib Yaar Tera Haye Kati Hero Laage Re
Bugle Ki Daal Chamka Ke Raakhe Daaki Kati Dholi Car Ne

Tochan King Kave Tere Yaar Ne Re Gori Tere Yaar Ne
Tochan King Kave Tere Yaar Ne Re Gori Tere Yaar Ne

Itihaas Ke Me Likha Jaaga Bhoole Koni Log Isa Kaam Kargya 
Hariyane Me Te Aake Chhora Delhi Ke Me Dekh Sehar Jaam Kargya
Fer Te Tu Bhej De Ne Dharti Pe Bhole Mhare Dildaar Ne

Tochan King Kave Tere Yaar Ne Re Gori Tere Yaar Ne
CK Nara Gaadi Ke Ma Raakhe Se Jhakoi Peni Talwaar Ne
Tochan King Kave Tere Yaar Ne Re Gori Tere Yaar Ne

snippet.title: 🎶 Bhajan Connect Thrissur | Pranathosmi – Ashtapathilayam | Raga Reethigowla Special Blend 🎶
snippet.description:
A magical evening from Bhajan Connect Thrissur—where devotion met creativity in Raga Reethigowla. This presentation brings together:

🎶 “Pranathosmi” – from the film Sindoora Rekha, written by Kaithapram, composed by Sharath sir, and immortalized by K.J. Yesudas (Dasettan).
🎶 “Ashtapathilayam” – written by Kalarkodu Chandran, composed by M.G. Radhakrishnan, and sung by Pattanakkadu Purushothaman.
✨ And in between—an unexpected non-devotional surprise blend, where Reethigowla takes a new, refreshing turn beyond tradition.

This unique mix celebrates the versatility of Raga Reethigowla, moving seamlessly from deep bhakti to artistic experimentation.

💫 Performed live by Nandagovindam Bhajans as part of our Bhajan Connect series, where audience voices and our music merge into one unforgettable experience.

🙏 If this journey touched you, don’t forget to Like, Share & Subscribe for more soulful and creative blends.

#BhajanConnect #Nandagovindam #Reethigowla #Pranathosmi #Ashtapathilayam #Yesudas #MGRadhakrishnan #Guruvayoorappan #MusicFusion

snippet.title: CRL25 Stats Royale - Gold Edition Finals | Day 2 | Clash Royale
snippet.description:
CRL25 | Stats Royale - Gold Edition Finals Day 2

Day 2 of the Stats Royale – Gold Edition has arrived, and the stakes have never been higher!

Only the strongest remain, clashing in heart-stopping battles that will shape the path to the World Finals. With the Golden Ticket on the line, each match could define a legacy.

Brace yourself for unforgettable plays, epic rivalries, and the rise of a true Stats Royale Champion.

🎙 Join the action with the legendary casters:

- Rich Slaton: https://x.com/RichSlaton
- Andrew Ghai: https://x.com/AndrewGhai
- JuicyJ: https://x.com/JuicyJCR
- Joshua Sharon: https://x.com/ahcraaaap

Who will rise? Who will conquer? The Stats Royale Champion will be crowned soon. 

#CRL25 #ClashRoyaleLeague #StatsRoyale #GoldenTicket

FOLLOW US ON:

- Twitter/X: https://twitter.com/EsportsRoyaleEN
- Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/esportsroyale
- CRL Website: https://esports.clashroyale.com
